%% =========================================================
%%                     Central Data Store
%% =========================================================
DB[(Central Data Store<br/>SQLite / SQLiteCloud Database<br/>DATABASE_URL)]:::central

DBT["Core Tables<br/><br/>• User (soldier/clerk/adjutant + approval)<br/>• LoginSession<br/>• FitnessPlan<br/>• AssignedPlan<br/>• FitnessTest<br/>• Report<br/>• IpftDate"]:::central

DB --- DBT

%% =========================================================
%%                     Surrounding Modules
%% =========================================================

SoldierModule["Soldier Module<br/><br/>• View fitness status<br/>• View assigned plan & exercises<br/>• View IPFT schedule/results<br/>• Profile/BMI view"]:::green

ClerkModule["Clerk Module<br/><br/>• Record fitness tests<br/>• Justify results<br/>• Assign plans<br/>• Send reports to adjutant<br/>• View analytics"]:::blue

AdjutantModule["Adjutant Module<br/><br/>• Approve soldiers<br/>• Set IPFT date<br/>• View reports<br/>• View high-risk soldiers<br/>• Dashboard analytics"]:::blue

AuthModule["Authentication Module<br/><br/>• Login<br/>• Signup<br/>• JWT token issue/verify<br/>• Password hashing (bcryptjs)<br/>• Session logging"]:::purple

FitnessModule["Fitness & Plans Module<br/>(Next.js APIs)<br/><br/>• Manage FitnessPlan<br/>• AssignedPlan<br/>• Status calculation<br/>• Charts/trends"]:::green

ReportsModule["Reports Module<br/><br/>• New-soldiers reports<br/>• Clerk reports<br/>• Read/mark reports"]:::purple

HighRiskModule["High-Risk Soldiers Module<br/><br/>• Identify 'Unfit' soldiers<br/>• Provide risk listing output"]:::red

BatchModule["Batch/Admin Scripts<br/><br/>• setup-cloud-db.mjs<br/>• add-sample-plan.mjs<br/>• import-soldiers-to-db.js<br/>• export-db-json.js<br/>• inspect-*.js<br/>• migrate-users-to-prisma.js"]:::gray

FileExports["File Exports / Seeds<br/><br/>• /exports/*.json<br/>• /data/users.json<br/>• /data/fitness-status.json<br/>• /data/users.db (legacy)"]:::yellow

%% =========================================================
%%                     Data-centric connections
%% =========================================================

SoldierModule <--> |read| DB
ClerkModule <--> |read/write| DB
AdjutantModule <--> |read/write| DB

AuthModule <--> |read/write User + LoginSession| DB
FitnessModule <--> |read/write plans + tests + assignments| DB
ReportsModule <--> |read/write Report| DB
HighRiskModule <--> |read User fitnessStatus| DB

BatchModule <--> |read/write| DB
BatchModule <--> |read/write| FileExports

